condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Sch 2.Sec I.A.5(c) | Description :Approved the consolidated Project annual procurement plan for such year, andimplement said annual procurement plan in a manner sati sfactory to the Association. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Sch 2.Sec I.A.7(b) | Description :Oct 31 each year, prepare and provide consolidated annual implementation planfor the next succeeding calendar year, together with t he financing plan | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Sch 2.Sec I.A.8 | Description :Require each district hospital to: (a) prepare plans for both long- andshort-term training; (b) submit such plans to the respective DOH and to the Association for their review and approval | Due Date:01-Sep-2009

Finance Agreement :Sch 2.Sec II.A.2 | Description :Recipient shall hold a mid-term review with the Association to evaluate theprogress in Project implementation and in achievement of the Project objectives. | Due Date :30-Dec-2011

Finance Agreement :Sch 2.Sec V.1 | Description :MOH shall: (a) complete a baseline survey under terms of reference acceptable tothe Association; and (b) provide the results of suc h survey to the Association for its review and comments. | Due Date :31-Dec-2008
